Package com.github.freddyyj.localizationapi

Class LanguageList

java.lang.Object
com.github.freddyyj.localizationapi.LanguageList
public class LanguageList
extends Object
list of all available language.

This class should be singleton, and created already in Core. Use Core.getAvailableLanguageList() instead of creating manually. This class reads "langlist.json" in jar file.

Author:
FreddyYJ_
